1
00:00:32,414 --> 00:00:35,091
It is good to make
this sacrifice

2
00:00:35,216 --> 00:00:38,705
where the sun can
look down and see you.

3
00:00:40,087 --> 00:00:44,753
It is a great privilege
to dance with the sun.

4
00:00:46,494 --> 00:00:48,770
The sacrifice will be hard,

5
00:00:48,895 --> 00:00:52,063
but you are strong... and brave.

6
00:01:01,170 --> 00:01:03,251
You will not give up,

7
00:01:03,376 --> 00:01:05,386
as I did not give up

8
00:01:05,511 --> 00:01:08,679
when my father brought
me to this place.

9
00:01:12,518 --> 00:01:14,285
Ah.

10
00:01:29,933 --> 00:01:35,137
Follow the sun...
All day and pray.

11
00:01:35,303 --> 00:01:37,472
If you are strong and true,

12
00:01:37,638 --> 00:01:40,752
your sacrifice will be rewarded

13
00:01:40,877 --> 00:01:43,311
and you will have a vision.

14
